Usage: write_ilm_eco_db [-help] [-cell <string>] {-dir <string> | -module_model_tag <string>}

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>                 # cell for which to write eco db
                               # (string, optional)
-dir <string>                  # directory name to write ilm eco db
                               # (string, optional)
-module_model_tag <string>     # tag name to use for SHDB (string, optional)